## Storage path guidance
If you are organizing local/export paths in your own environment, keep it safe and structured:

### Preferred logical path
````text
/storage/sdcard/public_html/0xmonti.net/
````

### Fallback path
````text
/storage/6364-3930/
````

Use these only in environments you control and where app permissions are properly managed.

