## PWA manifest example

````json
{
  "name": "MontiAI",
  "short_name": "MontiAI",
  "start_url": "/",
  "display": "standalone",
  "background_color": "#0b1020",
  "theme_color": "#0b1020",
  "description": "Interactive AI Progressive Web App",
  "icons": [
    {
      "src": "/icons/icon-192.png",
      "sizes": "192x192",
      "type": "image/png"
    },
    {
      "src": "/icons/icon-512.png",
      "sizes": "512x512",
      "type": "image/png"
    }
  ]
}
````

---

## Service worker goals
Your service worker should:

- cache app shell
- cache static assets
- provide offline fallback
- queue non-critical background sync
- avoid caching sensitive authenticated responses unless explicitly designed for it

